value.name: Wednesday Club
value.original_name: คนกลางแล้วไง
value.overview: "Wednesday Club" is a club of middle children who feel they haven't been accepted, that no one pays them any attention. There are seven members, Kong, Phali, Tam, May, Kun, Mac and Pheem, and one ironclad rule: members may not form romantic relationships with each other in order to maintain amity.
